description:
This is a 34 minute workout called 'Heart Health Month Series: Treadmill Walk - Easy to Follow Along | 30 Minutes' from the channel Sunny Health & Fitness.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/Walking.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Comfort Moves and The Mindful Walk vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.

-Slow down to stop
-Figure 4 stretch
-Calves Stretch (R/L)
